{"about": "Introduced in Lost Canvas, Crane Yuzuriha (\u9db4\u661f\u5ea7\u306e\u30e6\u30ba\u30ea\u30cf, Kurein no Yuzuriha) is the Crane (Grus) Silver Saint in The Lost Canvas. She is a student of Hakurei, the Lemurian master, and by implication trained with Aries Sion. She does not wear the Silver Cloth until reaching Sanctuary, and tends not to wear a mask like any other female saint.\n \n She first appears after the supposed death of Pegasus Tenma at the hands of Alone. She finds Tenma's dying body and Unicorn Yato who tried to attack her as he thought she was an enemy. However Yuzuriha reasoned with him and took him and Tenma to Jamir. When they arrived, she offered her blood, allowing her master Hakurei to repair the Unicorn Cloth. Shortly thereafter, she is sent to the Underworld with Yato to rescue the soul of Tenma, which was trapped by one of Hades' specters.\n \n (Source: Wikipedia)\n\n", "name": "Yuzuriha Crane", "image": "https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/characters/12/75001.jpg", "mangaography": [{"image": "https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/r/23x32/images/manga/5/163126.jpg?s=c60e699264cceec96b6cb2094d483b43", "link": "/manga/1047/Saint_Seiya__The_Lost_Canvas_-_Meiou_Shinwa", "name": "Saint Seiya: The Lost Canvas - Meiou Shinwa"}], "member-favorites": 17, "animeography": [{"image": "https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/r/23x32/images/anime/8/75546.jpg?s=a532cddc9e84b080f4e0aecbde9330ab", "link": "/anime/6171/Saint_Seiya__The_Lost_Canvas_-_Meiou_Shinwa", "name": "Saint Seiya: The Lost Canvas - Meiou Shinwa"}, {"image": "https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/r/23x32/images/anime/12/29597.jpg?s=9a6b38060967686f8277fd764633375a", "link": "/anime/9130/Saint_Seiya__The_Lost_Canvas_-_Meiou_Shinwa_2", "name": "Saint Seiya: The Lost Canvas - Meiou Shinwa 2"}], "name-japanese": "(\u9db4\u661f\u5ea7\u306e\u30e6\u30ba\u30ea\u30cf)", "voice-actors": [{"image": "https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/voiceactors/3/19717v.jpg", "link": "/people/149/Sanae_Kobayashi", "nam